# tf.divide

``` python
tf.divide(
    x,
    y,
    name=None
```

Defined in [`tensorflow/python/ops/math_ops.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.9/tensorflow/python/ops/math_ops.py).
